                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-264691046" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-264691046" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="264691046">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/aomixiaobai/">白胖子沉默</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2010-07-02</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">伯林最牛B的地方不是其观点的新颖或尖锐，而是其思路的清晰与对问题多角度的关照，读其书乃是一种享受，仿佛一把梳子，帮你梳理好自己的思路。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="950486484">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-950486484" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-950486484" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="950486484">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1800696/">龙泉冢</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-08-16</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">又读了一遍柏林的名文《两种自由概念》。积极自由确实常常以自由之名，行暴政之实。叹服柏林敏锐的洞察力。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

